item.title: GSoC part 10: finishing the button stack page
item.description: I can start this blog post by sharing the news that I have passed for my second evaluation! This means that I’m now on the last sprint towards the finish line, with ahead of me profile support and the welcome screen. Yes; you’ve read that correctly: I didn’t mention the button page. I managed to fix that this week and it’s now pending review and some final issues (more about that below).
